# Cleanliness (mandatory)

Follow [docs/cleanliness-and-organization.md](docs/cleanliness-and-organization.md).

## Must

- Keep the repository root thin — no orphan files or scratch notes
- One responsibility per module/service; prefer existing libraries
- Prefer `services/` + `apps/` for microservices; use `src/` only for single-app
- Delete unused placeholders or leave a clear README why they remain
- No dead code, commented-out blocks, or duplicate docs
- Register new docs in `docs/INDEX.md`
- English-only structure and file names

## PR bar

Leave the tree cleaner than you found it. See the checklist in the cleanliness doc.
